{"tid":467753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」失戀應該點算好？","createTime":"2017-11-13T18:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T19:50:27.000Z","uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d53250f2556bdf439c55dafdaf092bcec9a23170","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:58:23.000Z","msg":"大家係點走出失戀痛楚？<br />\n有無咩解決方法？<br />\n訓唔著的巴絲打不如一齊傾下計。<br />\n<br />\n利申：剛失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想而家半夜打比前度嘈住佢，求佢唔好離開我，<br />\n為免比人當痴線佬，不如大家傾下計。"},{"pid":"99a6982329dbd77e166bf3f89c2cba0e5d3fd4ae","tid":467753,"uid":61415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:02:16.000Z","msg":"搵過個"},{"pid":"39b958c8582203465fc45129f1330233ef0075d9","tid":467753,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:07:07.000Z","msg":"冰封三尺非一日之寒<br />\n<br />\n算啦 佢唔愛你就"},{"pid":"cc62924b42aec7e60b5d1a06135395001158c10d","tid":467753,"uid":95663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:08:13.000Z","msg":"做好自己，等下一個出現"},{"pid":"e4cb09abb77982e6827f432476c3197f9a72153a","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵過個</blockquote><br />\n我有諗過搵過個，但心入面好明白最愛係呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd9d8882fd8e782d927cfb510bf168e3e49a9c4","tid":467753,"uid":37710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:15:29.000Z","msg":"由時間沖淡一切會是最好的選擇，<br />\n&ldquo;有緣而來，無緣而去。&rdquo;<br />\n縱使心中痛苦，<br />\n但既然對方已覺緣盡，<br />\n又何必勉強挽留？<br />\n祝福你盡快脫離悲痛，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e38b279bc94d1410cd07d55fdae850779d510","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冰封三尺非一日之寒<br />\n<br />\n算啦 佢唔愛你就</blockquote><br />\n我知道佢已經無咁愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我只係愈黎愈愛佢"},{"pid":"e1ff2316235459e018f2a7d8e9fcb0c7e854a117","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由時間沖淡一切會是最好的選擇，<br />\n&ldquo;有緣而來，無緣而去。&rdquo;<br />\n縱使心中痛苦，<br />\n但既然對方已覺緣盡，<br />\n又何必勉強挽留？<br />\n祝福你盡快脫離悲痛，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你，我仲未看透點解會緣盡，說好了的一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b367d2ec332c026a7400c3ef0aa9910d3c3d55bb","tid":467753,"uid":37710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由時間沖淡一切會是最好的選擇，<br />\n&ldquo;有緣而來，無緣而去。&rdquo;<br />\n縱使心中痛苦，<br />\n但既然對方已覺緣盡，<br />\n又何必勉強挽留？<br />\n祝福你盡快脫離悲痛，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你，我仲未看透點解會緣盡，說好了的一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;沒有任何人會在無目的之下出現，<br />\n就如每片雪花落下都有它的原因。&rdquo;<br />\n可能她在你的人生中出現就是為了教會你一些事情，<br />\n當她的使命完成，<br />\n她就會離開。<br />\n只能說她可能不是你一生一世的對象，<br />\n你與她也緣盡至此。<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286ad454c9eb92f95fd6a2be7a65d9ca4e1a2b28","tid":467753,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:28:26.000Z","msg":"呢個世界冇最愛 因為會有下一個出現<br />\n等下沖淡下再重新生活<br />\n頹廢唔緊要 只要抱住改善自己嘅心<br />\n當你放低咗之後你就會發現仲有好多唔同嘅女仔<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"0eb51d8b50b5af1d8812663bee2f55f1504ebd45","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由時間沖淡一切會是最好的選擇，<br />\n&ldquo;有緣而來，無緣而去。&rdquo;<br />\n縱使心中痛苦，<br />\n但既然對方已覺緣盡，<br />\n又何必勉強挽留？<br />\n祝福你盡快脫離悲痛，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你，我仲未看透點解會緣盡，說好了的一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;沒有任何人會在無目的之下出現，<br />\n就如每片雪花落下都有它的原因。&rdquo;<br />\n可能她在你的人生中出現就是為了教會你一些事情，<br />\n當她的使命完成，<br />\n她就會離開。<br />\n只能說她可能不是你一生一世的對象，<br />\n你與她也緣盡至此。<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n流水很清楚惜花這個責任<br />\n真的身份不過送運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f83fc5c5e5e04c4677bf9cf882b6093ad1336e5","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界冇最愛 因為會有下一個出現<br />\n等下沖淡下再重新生活<br />\n頹廢唔緊要 只要抱住改善自己嘅心<br />\n當你放低咗之後你就會發現仲有好多唔同嘅女仔<br />\n加油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓唔著真係好慘，<br />\n我淨係想要佢一個。"},{"pid":"1fef5f005fc8ee31b15bce668774aaf4a85a500d","tid":467753,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:46:35.000Z","msg":"佢係咪有第二個或者已經放低咗你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aee08213fb961a3da92b75d5d28347d901d3d3","tid":467753,"uid":101548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪有第二個或者已經放低咗你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仲一直求佢回心轉意，<br />\n我都覺得自己好無用。"},{"pid":"e9e8dac8abbfbf4e5f67e4e9e441ddd8d4eea758","tid":467753,"uid":16720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"下個更可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}